_sText: First thanks for ewerybody who made this map possible. Lila- Original map and blueprints. Moonlight - A small edit. The_greate_dm - For a couple of ideas. This is a edit by me and i added some spots and locations. (See the screenshots) Its really cool i have test played it on a 20 slotted server but i think a 32 slot server will be good too. Note i will make a new skybox or something soon cuz the current is so not my skill level :) The new spots are a new area... A train and a zombie jail where zombies go if they fall of some places which makes the players life a lot easier and the zombies harder and they haveto use more teamwork. On the wall there are only the names of Phantom and Lila on the wall because Moonlight and DM didn't want their names there. Permission by wildcard77 Is there a server playing this map?
